{"tid":1596482,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭提晒水︰廢除中英聯合聲明，爭取完全自治","createTime":"2019-09-26T13:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T16:28:04.000Z","uid":108757,"like":49,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7609b3a53dedc58861f674f87372a57ab9d6bf","tid":1596482,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭話<span style=\"color: red;\">一國兩制唔等於自治</span>。<br />\n中國話<span style=\"color: red;\">聯合聲明係過時垃圾</span>。<br />\n如果係咁，我地就要同英國講︰<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除中英聯合聲明，進行全民公投，香港人自己選擇香港未來！</span></span>美國已經多次提水，抗爭目標係<span style=\"color: red;\">爭取主權</span>！將一切返回聯合聲明之前嘅處境，英國、美國、中國甚至台灣，都有權俾主權香港。更加，香港可以以上全部都唔要，變成一個<span style=\"color: red;\">自由港，完全自治</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個一定要不停講、不停宣傳，因為係所有人嘅未來，超越五大訴求同光復香港！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n[行動PO] 主動出擊 - 成立臨時政府 (民間議會、民間法庭、民間護衛隊)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eegqRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eegqRS</a>"},{"pid":"9d1745c57488816343cc64ab30d45ee62e24331a","tid":1596482,"uid":108757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:49:57.000Z","msg":"香港自治<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afbb0b3c15c9c4a6f603689a8c8f612f1beb5c1","tid":1596482,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb6ed1c964fca699b6ede0afe003a4d503d91677","tid":1596482,"uid":32505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:51:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a4e93db61b72d7a214b9c6a4db8ae84282ae47d","tid":1596482,"uid":108757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"唔要高度自治，要完全自治<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b56093daf1c36345789a2989e32f148dfe0b3f","tid":1596482,"uid":40625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,